*[[Julian Koster]] – bass guitar, accordion, musical saw, bowed banjo, keyboards, organ (1996–1998, 2013–2015){{sfn|Anon.|1998}}
*[[Scott Spillane]] – trumpet, flugelhorn, trombone, euphonium, horn arrangements, guitar (1996–1998, 2013–2015){{sfn|Anon.|1998}}
* [[Jeremy Barnes (musician)|Jeremy Barnes]] – drums, piano, organ (1996–1998, 2013–2015){{sfn|Anon.|1998}}
* [[Robert Schneider]] – guitar, keyboards (studio only), bass guitar (studio only), gamelan instruments (studio only), horn arrangements (1993–1995, 1997){{sfn|Clair|2022}}

